    "Specifically, we present important considerations for firms that plan to implement Gen AI solutions, organized around two key issues: the type of Gen AI input and the handling of Gen AI output.",
    "We follow the framework with a discussion of promising avenues for continued scholarly exploration.",
    "Different Gen AI solutions involve custom versus more general inputs (e.g., LLMs, LVMs).",
    "A custom Gen AI solution requires company-specific information, which may be supplemented with general information.",
    "For example, retailers might need to link the Gen AI to their own customer data."
